/path></svg> The Script</span><p class=3D"text-lg md:text-xl font-medium te=
xt-white italic leading-relaxed">"I want to be close to you, and right now =
I'm not feeling connected in the way I need. Instead of saying no, can we s=
pend 15 minutes actually talking? Not about problems =E2=80=94 just about y=
ou. What's been on your mind?"</p></div><div class=3D"grid md:grid-cols-2 g=
