V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z"></path></svg> The Script</span><p class=3D"text-lg md:te=
xt-xl font-medium text-white italic leading-relaxed">"I'm noticing I'm repl=
aying our conversation from earlier. My brain is looking for what I did wro=
ng. I'm going to write this down and then let it go. If it's actually impor=
tant, we can talk about it tomorrow when I'm not in this loop."</p></div><d=
iv class=3D"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm"><div><span class=3D"text-[10=
px] uppercase text-emerald-500 font-bold block mb-1">Tone to Use</span><spa=
